{"tid":2235614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] 佛羅里達川普呈領先狀態，拜登剉咧等！","createTime":"2020-10-08T23:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T11:30:23.000Z","uid":52658,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7c10bc36959434c809fb4ada5154099f89ce5c60","tid":2235614,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T23:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbxDRjo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbxDRjo.jpg&h=3c06ed74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrgATxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrgATxu.png&h=fdd900ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RF8fTzr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRF8fTzr.png&h=626d1895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢份民調係川普確診既期間進行<br />\n可見確診對川普係有幫助<br />\n不過因為之前辯論果排跌得大跨張<br />\n所以整體民調佛州同亞利桑納州拜登領先緊4趴<br />\n北卡羅萊羅萊納拜登領先緊2趴<br />\n喬治亞州同俄亥俄 川普卜就1趴以下<br />\n<br />\n贏唔贏到就要睇下之後果個月維唔維持到呢個幅度<br />\n加上琴日彭斯有無幫川普加分仲係未知數<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得川普連任可能性不大<br />\n因為<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuskkf5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffuskkf5.png&h=1095af06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21df8102f9dc4f07bfb7978a8ce756573f7f13f","tid":2235614,"uid":127575,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T23:26:31.000Z","msg":"拜登贏撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人準備滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77da9fbce19cda65793d9071f746440811ce0df8","tid":2235614,"uid":25858,